summary:
Ambitious and dedicated environment professional with special interest in corporate social responsibility, environmental education and sustainable initiatives. Thanks to my research and analytical skills, I can effectively manage projects from the beginning to a succesful end.

I am a result-oriented person that works accurately and delivers qualitative work. I am a flexible professional who embraces teamwork, but also enjoys working independently. I love to contribute to a better environment, not only in my personal life, but also by means of my carreer.
